room_title: Escape room "Asylum" by Room Raiders in West Palm Beach
room_address: 7104 S Military Trail, Lake Worth, FL 33463
room_description: You and your friends stumble upon an abandoned asylum. Not wanting to be the chicken of the group, you agree to their dare to go inside. The door slams behind you, locking you in. You have one hour to escape before you come face to face with whoever was left behind. Did I mention... you're not alone?
